# Production env vars baked into the Vite build.
# Edit this file, commit, push — GitHub Actions rebuilds and deploys.

# Google Analytics 4 Measurement ID. Looks like "G-XXXXXXXXXX".
# Leave empty to disable GA entirely (no gtag.js download, zero overhead).
# Find yours at: analytics.google.com → Admin → Data Streams → Web → Measurement ID
VITE_GA_ID=
